         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">6/7/88 ¶  ¶ By this post, dear Mr Dyer, you will receive a parcel of ferns, collected during his last travels in S. E. New Guinea by poor Mr C Hartmann, who  ¶ succumbed ¶  to fever in that terrible c...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">88.07.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Thiselton-Dyer</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Kew correspondence, Australia, Mueller, 1882-90, f. 255.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6/7/88<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Date stamped</seg>: Royal Gardens Kew 11. Aug. 88. <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annotation by [Thiselton-Dyer </seg>?]: And with list 14.8.88 (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">letter not found</seg>).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By this post, dear Mr Dyer, you will receive a parcel of ferns, collected during his last travels in S. E. New Guinea by poor Mr C Hartmann, who <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">succumbed</hi>
               </seg> to fever in that terrible clime.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Carl Hartmann died in Brisbane on 14 December 1887 (</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; ">Queenslander</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">, 17 December 1887, p. 965).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> This sad occurrence accounts for the imperfect state of the collection; but it is nearly half of all; the other portion I sent to Mr Carruthers, who is now working on Mr Forbes's ferns. As you meet Mr Carruthers often you can of course arrange with him about the naming. Absolute novelty seems hardly among these ferns, unless one <name key="Alsophila">Alsophila</name>. My retaining nothing here, shows my disinterestedness; but I asked Mr C., to send me back a little of any rare or new species.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Very busy for Exhibition now.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">Centennial International Exhibition, Melbourne, 1888-9.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Alsophila">Alsophila</name>
            </p>
